	(10870,1,'2014-10-11 14:23:15','2014-10-11 14:23:15','[fullwidth backgroundcolor=\"\" backgroundimage=\"\" backgroundrepeat=\"no-repeat\" backgroundposition=\"left top\" backgroundattachment=\"scroll\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_preview_image=\"\" overlay_color=\"\" overlay_opacity=\"0.5\" video_mute=\"yes\" video_loop=\"yes\" fade=\"no\" bordersize=\"0px\" bordercolor=\"\" borderstyle=\"solid\" paddingtop=\"40px\" paddingbottom=\"20px\" paddingleft=\"40px\" paddingright=\"40px\" menu_anchor=\"\" equal_height_columns=\"no\" hundred_percent=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">LSC organizes meetings and road shows in the major financial cities of the world as part of the public and investor relations work to assist in building strong corporate images for public and private organizations and to strengthen public perception of the client companies.</p>\n[/fusion_text][/fullwidth]','Investor Event Planning','','publish','open','open','','investor-event-planning','','','2014-10-11 14:23:15','2014-10-11 14:23:15','',0,'http://theme-fusion.com/avada_demos/portfolio/?page_id=10870',0,'page','',0),
	(10883,1,'2014-10-11 14:58:50','2014-10-11 14:58:50','[fullwidth backgroundcolor=\"yes\" backgroundimage=\"\" backgroundrepeat=\"no-repeat\" backgroundposition=\"left top\" backgroundattachment=\"scroll\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_preview_image=\"\" overlay_color=\"\" overlay_opacity=\"0.5\" video_mute=\"yes\" video_loop=\"yes\" fade=\"no\" bordersize=\"0px\" bordercolor=\"\" borderstyle=\"solid\" paddingtop=\"0px\" paddingbottom=\"0px\" paddingleft=\"40px\" paddingright=\"40px\" menu_anchor=\"\" equal_height_columns=\"no\" hundred_percent=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lion State Capital (\"LSC\") integrates venture capital and private equity exposure and expertise for growing businesses with public relations and investor relations.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">With representatives and associates in Europe, Asia and the Middle East, LSC works across virtually in the major financial cities of the world and are respected for the relationships we keep in assisting growing companies to access capital from venture capital and proven equity sources and investor event planning.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Founded in 2013, LSC functions as a boutique consultancy for the growing company or start ups in capital raising and strategy.</p>\n[/fusion_text][/fullwidth]','About Us','','publish','open','open','','about-us','','','2014-10-11 14:58:50','2014-10-11 14:58:50','',0,'http://theme-fusion.com/avada_demos/portfolio/?page_id=10883',0,'page','',0),
	(10885,1,'2014-10-11 14:59:15','2014-10-11 14:59:15','[fullwidth backgroundcolor=\"\" backgroundimage=\"\" backgroundrepeat=\"no-repeat\" backgroundposition=\"left top\" backgroundattachment=\"scroll\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_preview_image=\"\" overlay_color=\"\" overlay_opacity=\"0.5\" video_mute=\"yes\" video_loop=\"yes\" fade=\"no\" bordersize=\"0px\" bordercolor=\"\" borderstyle=\"solid\" paddingtop=\"40px\" paddingbottom=\"40px\" paddingleft=\"40px\" paddingright=\"40px\" menu_anchor=\"\" equal_height_columns=\"no\" hundred_percent=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]LSC provides a broad range of services in the venture capital sector; namely:-\n<ul>\n	<li>Specialized knowledge on how companies are formed, financed, grown and taken public or merged;</li>\n	<li>Guidance at all stages, from initial funding through IPOs and mergers;</li>\n	<li>Provision of legal support to company executive and managers with a single point of accountability</li>\n	<li>Guidance on business model issues, fundraising strategy and development of quality investor materials suitable for meaningful evaluation;</li>\n	<li>Invest in ‘off-the-clock’ meetings with management and the Board.</li>\n</ul>\nLSC is a premium private equity company and takes an integrated and pragmatic approach to investing in Asia, Europe and Middle East. LSC invests in a collection of partnerships positioning itself for growth across all sectors.\n\nImpartial and confident, LSC carefully secures stable yet value added investments.[/fusion_text][/fullwidth]','Expertise','','publish','open','open','','expertise','','','2014-10-11 14:59:15','2014-10-11 14:59:15','',0,'http://theme-fusion.com/avada_demos/portfolio/?page_id=10885',0,'page','',0),
